Effect of electronic excitation, structure and composition on the projected density of states. Representation of the projected density of states for (a) monoclinic LTO, (b) monoclinic La2TiZrO7, (c) cubic La2ZrTiO7, and (d) cubic LZO crystals without (solid lines) and with (dashed lines) 1.6% electronic excitation and no structural relaxation. The Fermi energy is referenced by a black dashed line at 0 eV.
